[C7]Would the world [F]hear your [C]reply
Are you walking and a-talking with the [G7]Lord
Would you stand and shout His [C]name 
[C7]Or [F]bow your head in [C]shame
Are you walking and [G7]a-talking with the [C]Lord
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 5}
repeat chorus
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 6}
When the time has come to go
[C7]Will your [F]robe be white as [C]snow
Are you walking and a-talking with the [G7]Lord
Will He take you by the [C]hand 
[C7]And [F]lead you to that promised [C]land
Are you walking and [G7]a-talking with the [C]Lord
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 7}
repeat chorus
{end_of_verse}
